text: Tommy Songo (born 20 April 1995) is a Liberian footballer who plays for LISCR, as a goalkeeper. ==Career== Born in Monrovia, Songo has played for LISCR. He made his international debut for Liberia in 2015. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Liberian footballers Category:Liberia international footballers Category:LISCR FC players Category:Association football goalkeepers
